title: The Deadline tune #3 (Demo tune 10) remix
info:
I decided to compose a remix of the Demo Tune 10 as it seems to named :) It's one tune of the The Deadline demo ( 2nd part music) released by Finnish Gold.
This is my first touch for C-64 music since 1990, so I've been out the scene 25 years:) time flies....
I played quitar and bass lines and for drums used Ez Drummer. Original C-64
 lines are spiced with some effects like Reverb, Delay, Wah and Chorus.
Enjoy and feel free to comment!
Cheers!
